                            <comment id="17228450" author="arturobernalg" created="Mon, 9 Nov 2020 09:29:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi&#160;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=RobertBudda&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;RobertBudda&quot;&gt;RobertBudda&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

